Hugh E. Wright https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hugh_E._Wright 0 Hugh E. Wright (13 April 1879 – 12 February 1940) was a French-born, British actor and screenwriter. He was the father of actor Tony Wright. Hugh_E._Wright ( 13_April_1879 – 12_February_1940 ) was a_French-born , British_actor_and_screenwriter . He was the_father of actor_Tony_Wright .
